original_title: Sunee Dhaliwal - Live at the Waldorf
overview: CTV’s Comedy Now | Just For Laughs | People’s Champ Winner | Sunee Dhaliwal’s brand new special was captured at the Waldorf Hotel’s legendary Cabaret Room. Sunee’s easy-going style will take you on a hilarious ride through his tall and twisted mind.
title: Sunee Dhaliwal - Live at the Waldorf
